creator: CosmosCreed
descriptionHtml:
Is "Cosmos Creed" just another shoot'em up (shmup)? absolutely NOT!While maintaining old-school essence "CosmosCreed" brings staggering visuals, a more realistic gameplay approach along with a stimulating original soundtrack that will keep you immersed throughout your journey of keeping the skies clear from enemy encroachments."

Features:
1- 3D top-down shooter
2- Variety of enemies and their arsenal
3- 11 unique levels of breath-taking environments
4- Each level incorporates 4 difficulty modes
5- Intuitive weapon's panel
6- Customized control modes
7- Comprehensive upgrade system and Powerups
8- well-designed sysematic and balanced upgrade system
9- Quality profiles to support almost every device in the market
10- An intimidating BOSS for each level
11- Vie for the top with your high score by bringing off objectives in every level
12- In-app purchases for the impatients to speed up their upgrades

creator: CosmosCreed
descriptionHtml:
Get ready for an unforgettable Shoot‘Em Up experience in our thrilling SHMUP game! With non-stop action and challenging gameplay, you'll be on the edge of your seat as you dodge and weave through waves of enemy spacecraft.
Our SHMUP game delivers all the classic elements of the genre, from intense action to addictive Shoot‘Em Up gameplay. Each level features waves of enemy ships, bullets, and lasers, making it essential to have quick reflexes and precise aim to survive.

As you progress through the game, you'll face even more challenging enemies and obstacles. But fear not, power-ups are scattered throughout each level, providing you with a temporary boost in your Shoot‘Em Up abilities.
With 11 levels of non-stop SHMUP 'action,' you'll be entertained for hours as you travel through space, facing off against enemy spacecraft in epic battles. The graphics and sound effects will immerse you in the game's world, adding to the adrenaline-fueled Shoot‘Em Up experience.

Our SHMUP game is perfect for fans of the genre and newcomers alike. The SHMUP genre has been a fan favorite for years, and our game delivers on all the aspects that make it so popular. The intense action addictive Shoot‘Em Up gameplay, and challenging levels will deliver on your expectations
The classic gameplay and challenging levels will test even the most seasoned Shoot‘Em Up player, while the power-ups provide a fun and exciting twist.

In addition to the non-stop action and thrilling Shoot‘Em Up gameplay, our shmup game also features an intuitive upgrade system that will enhance your weapons and abilities as you progress through the levels.

Upgrade your laser to increase its power duration, or upgrade your plane's guns to deal even more damage to enemy ships. And don't forget about the energy shield upgrade, which will give you a temporary boost in defense when you need it most.

The magnet upgrade is perfect for collecting power-ups and stars, while the missiles upgrade provides you with a powerful weapon to take down tougher enemies. And for those truly epic battles, the rocket barrage upgrade will give you the firepower you need to emerge victorious.

With each upgrade, your Shoot‘Em Up abilities will become stronger and more formidable. And the best part is that the upgrade system is easy to use and intuitive, allowing you to focus on the shmup action without getting bogged down in complicated menus or controls.

Upgrade your weapons and abilities to become the ultimate Shoot‘Em Up pilot and save the world from the enemy forces. With a variety of upgrades available, you can tailor your gameplay experience to your personal style, making each playthrough unique and exciting.

Experience the thrill of upgrading your weapons and abilities in our shmup game. Download it now and get ready for the ultimate Shoot‘Em Up adventure!

Don't wait any longer to experience the thrill of SHMUP 'action.' Download our game now and become the ultimate Shoot‘Em Up pilot and get ready for the ultimate adventure!

Get ready for an unforgettable Shoot‘Em Up experience in CosmosCreed! With non-stop action and challenging gameplay, you'll be on the edge of your seat as you dodge and weave through waves of unique enemies.
It delivers all the classic elements of the genre, from intense action to addictive Shoot‘Em Up gameplay. Each level features waves of enemy ships, bullets, and lasers, making it essential to have quick reflexes and precise aim to survive.

As you progress through the game, you'll face even more challenging enemies and obstacles. But fear not, power-ups are scattered throughout each level, providing you with a temporary boost in your abilities.
With 11 levels of non-stop SHMUP 'action,' you'll be entertained for hours as you travel through space, facing off against enemies in epic battles. The graphics and sound effects will immerse you in the game's world, adding to the adrenaline-fueled experience.

The classic gameplay and challenging levels will test even the most seasoned player, while the power-ups provide a fun and exciting twist.
It also features an intuitive upgrade system that will enhance your weapons and abilities as you progress through the levels.

Upgrade your laser to increase its power duration, or upgrade your plane's guns to deal even more damage to enemy ships. And don't forget about the energy shield upgrade, which will give you a temporary boost in defense when you need it most.

The magnet upgrade is perfect for collecting power-ups and stars, while the missiles upgrade provides you with a powerful weapon to take down tougher enemies. And for those truly epic battles, the rocket barrage upgrade will give you the firepower you need to emerge victorious.

With each upgrade, your abilities will become stronger and more formidable. And the best part is that the upgrade system is easy to use and intuitive, allowing you to focus on the shmup action without getting bogged down in complicated menus or controls.

Upgrade your abilities to become the ultimate pilot and save the world from the enemy forces. With a variety of upgrades available, you can tailor your gameplay experience to your personal style, making each playthrough unique and exciting.

Download it now and get ready for the ultimate Shoot‘Em Up adventure!
